						<div class="postbody">Nevermind, I'll answer myself. I found another doc that goes into much better detail about the PPU. It's 3 CPU cycles per PPU cycle, but it looks like I need to re-write my PPU logic to work on a per-cycle basis instead of a per-scanline one.
<br />
<br />Although I do wonder if emulators properly drop the odd cycle on scanline 20 of every odd frame (NTSC color burst stuff)..</div>

